091F8A44.Line13.6DE47: I don’t care what she showed you. Please, let’s just get out of here.

2AFFCA44.Line7.B6582: I opened the way for Lilith, but I could not pass through with her. I...I lack the divine element, you see?

5E6F16B0.Line21.B6582: I will finish these runes with your blood.

722D41CF.Line11.B6582: My little magpie, she awakened me. She showed me things...I can’t even put into words. Once I’ve finished, you will understand...

8D3EA915.VoiceDir17.6DE47: extertion sounds, trying to break away

910B50C2.Line5.B6582: You’re just in time. Beyond this lake lies the Necropolis of the Firstborn. A trove of magic and knowledge.

97E4E651.VoiceDir31.6DE47: exertion from getting blasted by magic

A61634D3.Line15.B6582: Oh. I see. Yes...clever magpie. Trying to lead me away so you can take all this for yourself? Hmm?
